<h2>Apply to the Summer 2013 Batch of Hacker School</h2>
<p>
Apply by <strong>Thursday, March 28 at 11:59 PM ET</strong> to be guaranteed an admissions decision by Friday, April 26.
(For more details, see
<a href="/faq#admissions-timeline-question" target="_blank">our admissions timeline</a>.)
</p>
<p>In general, clear and concise answers are better than long ones. Most answers have a 1500 character max length, but you don't need to write that much. All fields are required.</p>
